    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "a panic attack? i don't feel particularly anxious, just uncomfortable. and i dont really have time to go to the doctor or wait for a call back right now. it really feels like just indigestion though, like that heavy feeling you get after eating a lot. do you think it's worth the trip to the er if i just take an antacid and see if it goes away in 20 mins?",
