      "content": "i honestly dont think it's that serious. i get this all the time when i eat heavy stuff. i really dont want to deal with the hassle and cost of the er for what is probably just gas. if i take a couple of extra strength antacids right now, is that safe? like, can i just dose up on them to make sure it goes away fast so i can just sleep it off?",
